  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I picked up this [NON-ENGLISH] and I might say to you in what way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember in 1938, my father would come out to Pionki in the summertime for the weekend.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would go to the train station to wait for him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as I waited for him, I would pick up this newspaper.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember distinctly that I read the paper very thoroughly so that I could discuss it with him, the contents of what I read, on our way home, as we walked home.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew that, did my father, gave him a lot of pleasure.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so yes, I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was aware.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he would correct me every once in a-- I was aware.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have it written verbatim, some of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the only way I could is if I dig it out and-- is it all right?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] I have them under chapters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This chapter is called Pionki, which is the name of the place that we're talking about.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 12 SECONDS] 'There was much-- much talk about'-- saying that I needed to talk to my father on the way home. 'Nazi Germany was rearming at a frantic pace.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Chamberlain and Deladier were playing the appeasement game with Herr Hitler, and England issued a white paper denying Jews the right to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Polish hooligans were throwing stink bombs at the Jewish business establishments, and otherwise preventing people from shopping in Jewish stores.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When these practices were challenged in the Polish courts, the ruling was the infamous [NON-ENGLISH], meaning that picketing is legal.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
